{
  "title": "Comparing Potential Energy of Attractions",
  "publicationStatus": "public",
  "labEnvironment": "production",
  "subtitle": "Explore the difference in attractive forces between polar and non-polar molecules.",
  "category": "",
  "subCategory": "",
  "screenshot": "",
  "aspectRatio": 1.5,
  "fontScale": 1,
  "lang": "en-US",
  "i18nMetadata": "",
  "credits": "",
  "helpOnLoad": true,
  "aboutOnLoad": false,
  "about": [
    "Explore the change in potential energy when molecules are separated from each other.",
    "",
    "First, choose a pair of molecules or atoms from the drop-down menu and \"pull\" on the green star to separate them.",
    "Then, compare observations of the potential energy of each molecule or scenario tested.",
    "***",
    "*This simulation was developed by [the Interactions project](https://concord.org/projects/interactions \"the Interactions Project\") ",
    "with funding from the National Science Foundation (DRL-1232388) in partnership with ",
    "[the CREATE for STEM Institute](http://create4stem.msu.edu/ \"the CREATE for STEM Institute\") at Michigan State University. To learn more, ",
    "[visit the Interactions curriculum collection](https://learn.concord.org/interactions \"visit the Interactions curriculum collection\") in ",
    "which this simulation is embedded.*"
  ],
  "theme": "",
  "showTopBar": true,
  "showBottomBar": true,
  "padding": 10,
  "models": [
    {
      "type": "md2d",
      "id": "npPulling",
      "url": "models/lab-version/1/md2d/interactions/comparing-potential-energy-of-bond/npPulling.json",
      "onLoad": [
        "start(); setPairwiseLJProperties(0, 2, { epsilon: 0 }); ",
        "set('breakEnergy',10.5);",
        "set('finalPotential',33);",
        "set('potentialFactor',15);",
        "callEvery(25, function() {",
        "  var x1 = getAtomProperties(0).x,",
        "      y1 = getAtomProperties(0).y,",
        "      x2 = getAtomProperties(3).x,",
        "      y2 = getAtomProperties(3).y,",
        "      distx = x1-x2,",
        "      disty = y1-y2,",
        "      distance = Math.pow((distx*distx)+(disty*disty),0.5)-0.19;",
        "  set('countPotential', get('finalPotential')-get('potentialFactor')*Math.pow(distance,-0.167)+get('breakEnergy'));",
        "});"
      ],
      "viewOptions": {
        "controlButtons": "",
        "enableKeyboardHandlers": false,
        "imageMapping": {
          "star.png": "star.svg"
        },
        "textBoxes": [
          {
            "x": 0.4,
            "y": 1.7,
            "fontSize": 0.12
          }
        ]
      },
      "modelOptions": {
        "useDuration": false
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "md2d",
      "id": "polarPulling",
      "url": "models/lab-version/1/md2d/interactions/comparing-potential-energy-of-bond/polarPulling.json",
      "onLoad": [
        "start();setPairwiseLJProperties(0, 2, { epsilon: 0 }); ",
        "set('breakEnergy',10);",
        "set('finalPotential',28.5);",
        "set('potentialFactor',8);",
        "callEvery(25, function() {",
        "  var x1 = getAtomProperties(0).x,",
        "      y1 = getAtomProperties(0).y,",
        "      x2 = getAtomProperties(3).x,",
        "      y2 = getAtomProperties(3).y,",
        "      distx = x1-x2,",
        "      disty = y1-y2,",
        "      distance = Math.pow((distx*distx)+(disty*disty),0.5)-0.05;",
        "  set('countPotential', get('finalPotential')-get('potentialFactor')*Math.pow(distance,-0.5)+get('breakEnergy'));",
        "});"
      ],
      "viewOptions": {
        "controlButtons": "",
        "enableKeyboardHandlers": false,
        "imageMapping": {
          "star.png": "star.svg"
        },
        "textBoxes": [
          {
            "x": 0.4,
            "y": 1.7,
            "fontSize": 0.12
          }
        ]
      },
      "modelOptions": {
        "useDuration": false
      }
    }
  ],
